annotations.description: The Eastside is one of those crowd pleasing drinks that everyone loves. It was created by George Delgado of Libation in New York City around 2004. The drink ...
annotations.title: Modern Classic: Eastside

textContent:
2oz or 60ml Gin
1oz or 30ml Lime Juice
.75ml or 20ml Simple Syrup
6-8 Mint Leaves
2 Cucumber Slices

Add ingredients to shaker. 
Muddle. 
Shake and double strain.
